first island adventure.

03:05.051 --> 03:07.019
Dude, we're sick of
island adventures.

03:07.021 --> 03:08.120
Yeah, they're really lame.

03:08.321 --> 03:09.621
Ha! Lame?

03:09.623 --> 03:11.490
Island adventures aren't lame.

03:11.492 --> 03:12.925
You guys just
need to be reminded

03:12.927 --> 03:14.560
of how much fun
we've had this week

03:14.562 --> 03:17.062
