<i>is actually fake ♪</i>

04:06.713 --> 04:08.981
Wait a minute.
This island is fake?

04:09.816 --> 04:12.851
(GASPS) The song was right.
The trees are fake.

04:13.920 --> 04:16.488
They all are. How did we
not notice that before?

04:16.789 --> 04:18.890
Because we've never
walked behind them I guess.

04:18.892 --> 04:21.360
Only the weirdos would
walk behind the trees.

04:22.095 --> 04:23.829
Is anything real here?

04:24.530 --> 04:26.298
The rocks are foam!

04:26.300 --> 04:27.499
(GASPS)

04:27.501 --> 04:29.768
The banana has the
microphone inside.

04:29.770 --> 04:30.869
(GASPS)

04:30.871 --> 04:33.205
I think this crab is
actually a camera.

04:33.606 --> 04:34.806
(GASPS)

04:35.041 --> 04:37.776
The freckle on my butt
looks like Mickey Mouse!

04:38.978 --> 04:40.946
Looks more like a
meatball sub if you ask me.

04:41.381 --> 04:44.449
I believe it's the unicorn
upon its cloud of dreams.

04:44.617 --> 04:47.019
Okay, clearly,
it's a human skull.

04:47.253 --> 04:48.520
Enough about the freckle!

04:48.688 --> 04:50.789
