two bears high-fiving.

04:51.024 --> 04:52.891
(ALL CHATTER IN AGREEMENT)

04:52.893 --> 04:54.159
They're girl bears.

04:54.161 --> 04:56.094
Now, as crazy as it sounds,

04:56.096 --> 04:59.431
I think this is a stage
and we are being watched.

05:00.700 --> 05:02.034
We need to find a way out.

05:02.669 --> 05:03.802
How about through there?

05:04.904 --> 05:06.705
A hatch. That's it!

05:06.707 --> 05:11.143
Something tells me that this
is the start of another
Island Adventure.

05:11.377 --> 05:13.278
-(ALL GROAN)
-Ugh.

05:15.581 --> 05:17.015
<i>♪ Island adventure! ♪</i>

05:19.886 --> 05:21.186
