over the entire island.

05:28.062 --> 05:30.228
And they've been recording
our every move.

05:30.863 --> 05:32.998
Aloha, Titans!

05:33.000 --> 05:34.766
Control Freak.

05:34.768 --> 05:38.170
I should have known the master
of media manipulation
was behind this.

05:38.172 --> 05:40.105
While you were on your
little pleasure cruise,

05:40.107 --> 05:42.341
I captured your boat,
wiped your memories,

05:42.343 --> 05:43.475
placed you on a fake island

05:43.477 --> 05:45.477
inside this giant
viewing arena

05:45.479 --> 05:47.713
and suppressed
your powers. Ah!

05:48.381 --> 05:49.514
But why?

05:49.516 --> 05:50.882
I was starting to get bored

05:50.884 --> 05:52.517
watching you
in your normal environment.

05:52.519 --> 05:55.620
Living room, kitchen.
Living room, kitchen.

05:55.622 --> 05:57.689
It's so repetitive
and predictable.

05:57.691 --> 05:59.691
Hey! Sometimes we
goes to the roof.

05:59.693 --> 06:00.859
And the lawn.

06:00.861 --> 06:04.029
Ooh! The lawn.
How exciting!

06:04.031 --> 06:05.330
I just thought it
would be interesting

06:05.332 --> 06:08.600
if you did something,
you know, interesting
for once.

06:08.602 --> 06:10.635
Like, you know,
an island setting.

06:11.637 --> 06:12.771
Howdy!

06:12.773 --> 06:16.775
Sorry, but this maniacal
mini-series is over,
Control Freak.

06:16.943 --> 06:19.478
Yeah! We want to get back
to our normal setting.

06:19.480 --> 06:21.380
-The living room.
-And the kitchen.

06:21.382 --> 06:22.781
And sometimes the roof.

06:22.783 --> 06:24.416
Don't forget the lawn.

06:24.418 --> 06:27.486
All right. But your
audience won't be happy.

06:27.488 --> 06:28.587
Audience?

06:28.589 --> 06:30.322
(LAUGHING) This show
wasn't just for me.

06:30.324 --> 06:33.792
