who despise us

06:49.076 --> 06:51.977
devote so much of the time
and energy to watching us?

06:52.145 --> 06:54.246
Girl, have you been
on the Internet?

06:54.248 --> 06:56.047
-CYBORG: Brutal, brutal. Stop!
-(BABY CRYING)

06:56.049 --> 06:58.083
RAVEN: Why are people so mean?
