the opinions of people
on the Internet

07:01.488 --> 07:04.089
aren't accurate indicators of
popularity or success.

07:04.091 --> 07:05.257
Anyway,

07:05.259 --> 07:06.958
you can try and stop the show,

07:06.960 --> 07:08.560
but they won't let you!

07:08.562 --> 07:10.328
Ha-ha, not without a fight.

07:11.898 --> 07:14.733
(HECKLING)

07:15.568 --> 07:17.436
Man! Look at all of them.

07:17.438 --> 07:19.938
Ooh! This is going to be good.

07:19.940 --> 07:22.040
